reviewText: Have enjoyed the office from the beginning. Holidays are especially great.  Thoroughly enjoyed this video.  Have told my friends.  two have asked to borrow it.  good fun.

reviewText: I know there aren't any big extras and yes, I have all these episodes on DVD because I own all the seasons. I still love this DVD! It was great to be able to pop it in and watch them all back to back. I'm keeping it with the rest of my Christmas DVDs and will watch it at least once every year!
summary: So fun to have all the Christmas shows in one place

reviewText: If you like "the office" and if you like Christmas then this is the DVD set for you.  The first episode in this set is my favorite (Jenna Fischer aka Pam looks super hot in that red sweater) but all of the episodes are funny! Enjoy!

reviewText: Yes this is totally a commercially crass way to make a buck by pacakging four Christmas episodes with no extra features on to one disk when they are available elsewhere. But as one reveiwer mentioned, you have the convenience of having all the episodes one disk and the luxury of just popping that disk in to watch during the season.  The price is less than $8.00 and you can probably get it for less than that used.  Plus the Christmas episodes are some of the funniest episodes the show has produced.
